arStrings.szText: “I found your lost friend alive. He needs to be taken to a healer.”
Oh, I... I can’t believe it. I... if I knew he lived, I... I would have gathered a group... oh, I never should have run.
Bewildered. Mixed emotions of relief, anxiety, and panic. He's relieved Derin is alive, but is also worried Derin will blame him for leaving Derin behind.
(cough) It’s okay, Mateen. I just want to leave this place.
Derin is wounded and pained, but still makes an effort to comfort Mateen's panic.
Easy, I’ll help you to the healer, eh?
Less panicked than before. He's more concerned about Derin's condition than his own feelings.
Thank you, wanderer. You’re braver than most. Akarat must guide your path.
